      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just staring at the stars and it hit me how nothing actually matters. like, in a billion years the sun is just gonna swallow everything and none of this—the pain, the effort, all the people I've lost—it's all just going to be gone. it feels like we're just playing a game that doesn't even have a score. why even bother trying to keep going when the end result is always just empty silence?",
